395
00:20:59,208 --> 00:21:02,625
[Beth] <i>No, no, she wouldn't do this to me.
Leave without telling me?</i>

396
00:21:02,708 --> 00:21:03,541
[Rob] <i>Really?</i>

397
00:21:03,625 --> 00:21:06,708
How many times on a night out did
