464
00:24:36,916 --> 00:24:38,291
I'm so sorry.

465
00:24:38,375 --> 00:24:39,791
[footsteps approaching]

466
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:41,750
[Zain] Hey.

467
00:24:42,083 --> 00:24:43,583
