681
00:37:33,958 --> 00:37:36,976
- I just told you. He's the taxi driver.
- Who you were going to dinner with.

682
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,625
Give me a break. He's been helping me.

683
00:37:38,708 --> 00:37:43,250
