714
00:39:01,916 --> 00:39:03,208
Oh my God!

715
00:39:04,916 --> 00:39:06,458
[crying]

716
00:39:09,791 --> 00:39:10,791
[sniffles]

717
00:39:13,625 --> 00:39:14,625
